Title: The Last Time I Saw Paris
Description: Charles Wills returns to Paris to reminisce about the life he led there after it was liberated. He worked then for "Stars and Stripes" when he met both Marion and Helen Ellswirth. He soon married and was happy staying in Paris after his discharge. While working for a news organization, Charlie began to write the great novel that would come between him, his wife, and his daughter.
Short Description: An American journalist returns to Paris - a city that gave him true love and deep grief.
